description.en: EZOOW is a blockchain booking solution that facilitates an easy way to travel. By booking all travel methods in one platform without the complexity of conventional online brick and mortar booking and payment sites, the Ezoow application is designed to book and reserve flight tickets, hotels, train tickets and taxi service with its own cryptocurrency utilized to transact payments. Ezoow users will receive discounts on air, transportation fares, lodging and accommodation rates, credited extra token rewards from referrals that can be applied to future travel bookings.
